{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I did, I just took the star off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had it on my outer coat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just didn't wear the coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just did-- and went swimming and did the things that I liked to do anyhow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean nobody-- my parents didn't know about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because I didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just, well, why should all of a sudden give this up?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then the children, my friends began to change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the end of that too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't want to be my friends any longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only friends I have left-- I had left were Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a very good friend called Barbel Gottschalk, and she was deported to Warsaw in 1940.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember going with her to the place where we were-- where they were gathering, and I was carrying her backpack.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember saying good-bye to her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- we corresponded, and I did send her packages for a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I understand she was killed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the reason we stayed in Germany as long as we did is because my father was working for this Jewish organization, and he also had won the Iron Cross fighting for Germany in World War I.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know why, but they gave him some privileges for that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had-- two of his brothers, two of my uncles who died, were killed in World War I, fighting for Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were-- but because of that, they, they gave us some privileges.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the main privilege was going to Theresienstadt rather than another-- than a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also we stayed in Germany until the end of '42.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
